---
title: Indonesian-Style Chicken Tenders and Stir-Fried Noodles with Fried Eggs and Crispy Shallots
description: This plate of stir-fried noodles is inspired by the popular Indonesian dish 'mie goreng.' A sweet-and-savoury sauce coats fresh chow mein noodles, vibrant veggies and hearty chicken. Finishing touches of crispy shallots and a fried egg ensure every bite is oh-so-satisfying!
